-- Chrysler says UAW deal includes health care trust
-- 
-- Wed Oct 10, 2007 6:05pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/10/us-chrysler-deal-idUSN1029578220071010

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Chrysler LLC said on Wednesday the tentative labor deal it reached with the United Auto Workers union includes a health care trust. 

 The automaker said the agreement, which is subject to review by the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission, would improve Chrysler's manufacturing competitiveness. (Reporting by  Poornima Gupta )